locality: Ningjing Shan, Markham Range, between Mekong and Yangtze river drainages, E of Markam (Markham) ca. 50 km toward Batang (Sichuan), W of the Jinsha Jiang (Yantze River) ca. 16 km, ca. 750 km E of Lhasa, ca. *3376.
Qionglai Shan, Shou Lougou, tributary valley of Somang Qu (Rv.), ca. 40 km W of Weizhou, ca. 120 km NW Chengdu, k.p. 820.
NW of Luhuo along highway 317; between Luhuo and Ganzi (Garze) on S side of Xianshui He (Da Qu).
Confluence of nearly dry tributary and Yalong Jiang at intersection of road from Ganzi to Xinlong (highway 217) and road to Baiyu, just downstream from the village of Acha Echa).
